prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook: AI Application Development Ecosystem
prompt.content:
---

Promptbook is an ecosystem of projects and tools for writing AI applications using a human-understandable markup language called Book. It includes a VSCode plugin, Docker image, and support for various AI models.
